Irate students have murdered a Christian female student of Shehu Shagari College of Education in Sokoto on Thursday morning over alleged blasphemy. The deceased, identified only as Ms Deborah, was accused of passing unflattering comments about Prophet Mohammed (SAW) on the college campus. Following immediate threats to her safety, she was immediately evacuated to the security post of the school, according to a student who witnessed the development. But the mob pursued her to the security post and overpowered the personnel on duty. A video of how she was murdered and set ablaze has already gone viral on the social media. Authorities of the college have issued a statement announcing immediate closure of the school over the fracas that broke out following the incident. Details Laterâ€¦